Handlers should be unique in the playbook
Handlers get executed after all the task runs 
handlers get executed if changes are made in  notify part 
#######################################################################################
	example1
######################################################################################
This playbook reboots the hosts if "Reboot me now" is present in /var/tmp/reboot 
## First Run - 
[tamesh@ansibleserver notify_handlers]$ ansible-playbook  example1.yaml -i my_inventory

PLAY [Playbook to show sample of notify and handlers] **************************************************************************************************************************************************************

TASK [Gathering Facts] *********************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
ok: [centos]

TASK [Ensure content is present] ***********************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
changed: [centos]

TASK [Ensure the VM centos is connected] ***************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
ok: [centos]

RUNNING HANDLER [Reboot the server] ********************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
changed: [centos]

PLAY RECAP *********************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
centos                     : ok=4    changed=2    unreachable=0    failed=0    skipped=0    rescued=0    ignored=0

[tamesh@ansibleserver notify_handlers]$ ansible-playbook  example1.yaml -i my_inventory

PLAY [Playbook to show sample of notify and handlers] **************************************************************************************************************************************************************

TASK [Gathering Facts] *********************************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
ok: [centos]

TASK [Ensure content is present] ***********************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
ok: [centos]

TASK [Ensure the VM centos is connected] ***************************************************************************************************************************************************************************
